citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"依家有幾多巴士司機要超時工作？"},{"pid":"1c193f06674139e2eedd7f04fef8ba84c40675d9","tid":410402,"uid":92856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"問題起個掣度"},{"pid":"eae2d86b5672810ddb8d8403038c688e39fe5b89","tid":410402,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明係dc9玩野 做乜變左巴士佬踩幾多個鐘</blockquote><br />\n巴士佬冇保持行車距離，架的士佬突然減速，如果直撞可能司機死。"},{"pid":"78fd27ee0552ac730010cd43fc8e49c3d10e350a","tid":410402,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:56:42.000Z","msg":"早就應該立法最高工時，唔比用錢代替 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de996f8496edaefaab035d65cf41fd05468b176","tid":410402,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1ed1b05141e12eb21e8f7a5f69ca8427945528c","tid":410402,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa033103990d036d32961183327dec5dc9e547e5","tid":410402,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>明明係dc9玩野 做乜變左巴士佬踩幾多個鐘</blockquote><br />\n巴士佬冇保持行車距離，架的士佬突然減速，如果直撞可能司機死。</blockquote><br />\n根本就係巴士佬跟太貼"},{"pid":"509c10fc446e97f6497c45cf40ed3ab6a14193d0","tid":410402,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>明明係dc9玩野 做乜變左巴士佬踩幾多個鐘</blockquote><br />\n巴士佬冇保持行車距離，架的士佬突然減速，如果直撞可能司機死。</blockquote><br />\n根本就係巴士佬跟太貼</blockquote><br />\n跟得貼因為工時長"},{"pid":"90b33005343fe297996edc4a969c7606388ed8a9","tid":410402,"uid":19287,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外國大把地立已經立左法唔允許巴士佬連續工作X小時<br />\n一日最高工時都定左<br />\n香港呢方面好撚落後, 一句經濟發展就好似執到寶咁</blockquote><br />\n反而大陸對工人d保障多到嚇走d廠<br />\n大陸反而官貪得黎都做小小對人民好政績出黎<br />\n香港班官就反而不停壓榨市民去討好北京同商人去為自己退休鋪路"},{"pid":"ded3b5ad5ed98ef6959af0896b2179c94a456b89","tid":410402,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:00:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早就應該立法最高工時，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔比用錢代替</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把港豬會反對，唔好話僱主，大把打工仔都唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真係唔太可行<br />\n無記錯法國好似嘈到改返可以俾錢OT...好似係"},{"pid":"7f00ddc2ebbdd58cd90e1ed035f23725d69b8b16","tid":410402,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>明明係dc9玩野 做乜變左巴士佬踩幾多個鐘</blockquote><br />\n巴士佬冇保持行車距離，架的士佬突然減速，如果直撞可能司機死。</blockquote><br />\n根本就係巴士佬跟太貼</blockquote><br />\n跟得貼因為工時長</blockquote><br />\n想跟衝燈尾, 早D收工返去抖掛"},{"pid":"7920b79149bec48d8de320947d43af7976dad975","tid":410402,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"894a2c4287aea3f356634ff546d3d92bb9de9298","tid":410402,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸長啲時間有另外津貼 <br />\n諗呢個政策都on9</blockquote><br />\n可能請小d人嘛"},{"pid":"d1d87a4d378c03b7de2fb46279e711e5149e8f01","tid":410402,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早就應該立法最高工時，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔比用錢代替</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把港豬會反對，唔好話僱主，大把打工仔都唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 呢d仆街制度行左咁多年 唔明點解以前d人都忍到 真係返工可以重要過其他一切生活咩"},{"pid":"3b1c04cb2f799c2024d720a4fe2f581712b48343","tid":410402,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b